c: 2
v: 158
t: "“Ndithudi, Safaa ndi Marwa ndizizindikiro zolemekezera chipembedzo cha Allah. Choncho, amene akukachita mapemphero a Hajj ku nyumbayo, kapena kuchita Umrah, sikulakwa kwa iye kuzungulira pamenepo (pakati pamapiri amenewo). Ndipo amene achite chabwino modzipereka (adzalipidwa). Ndithudi Allah Ngothokoza; Ngodziwa"